            The hierarchical relationship matters: SEO is the technical and authority foundation that both AEO and GEO build on. AEO is a focused subset of GEO, targeting the specific direct-answer mechanisms of featured snippets and voice assistants. GEO is the umbrella discipline that covers all AI search surfaces, including the generative, synthesised responses that represent the most significant shift in how people access information online.
          </p>
          <p>
            For a direct comparison of GEO and traditional SEO specifically, see our <a href="/geo-vs-seo/" class="text-accent-400 underline decoration-accent-500/30 underline-offset-2 hover:text-accent-300">GEO vs SEO guide</a>.
